sentence: On Friday, MSC Industrial Direct ( MSM ) earned a positive adjustment to its Relative Strength ( RS ) Rating , from 69 to 74.
[ibd-display-video id=2881825 width=50 float=left autostart=true] IBD's unique rating identifies market leadership with a 1 (worst) to 99 (best) score.
The rating shows how a stock's price performance over the trailing 52 weeks compares to all the other stocks in our database.
Decades of market research reveals that the best stocks tend to have an 80 or higher RS Rating in the early stages of their moves.
See if MSC Industrial Direct can continue to show renewed price strength and clear that threshold.
